dct_title_s: Complete map of the rail roads and water courses, in the United States & Canada
dct_description_sm: In lower margin of main map is printed "Entered, according to act of Congress, in the year 1859 ..." At the bottom edge below the inset neat lines is printed "Entered, according to act of Congress, in the year 1861 by Charles Magnus ..." Description derived from published bibliography. Insets: Military map of Maryland & Virginia. 11 x 19 cm. -- Map of northern military movements: between New York & St. Louis. 14 x 24 cm. -- [View of the U.S. Capitol] 18 x 19 cm. -- [Entrance to Mobile Bay] 18 x 13 cm. -- [United States and the Gulf of Mexico] 18 x 18 cm. Prime meridian: Washington.
